<p><b>Civil society</b> is composed of the totality of voluntary civic and social organizations and institutions that form the basis of a functioning <a href="/wiki/Society" title="Society">society</a> as opposed to the force-backed structures of a <a href="/wiki/State" title="State">state</a> (regardless of that state's political system) and commercial institutions of the <a href="/wiki/Market" title="Market">market</a>.</p>
