<div style="margin-right: 20px;"><a name="Civil_society_scholars" id="Civil_society_scholars"></a>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Civil_society&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Civil society scholars">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Civil society scholars</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Benjamin_Barber" title="Benjamin Barber">Benjamin Barber</a></li>
